notes "
    To use in Neovim with lspconfig it is sufficient to specify cmd:

    require'lspconfig'.cmake.setup \{
        cmd = \{\"${prefix}/bin/cmake-language-server\"\};
    \}

    See other ways https://github.com/regen100/cmake-language-server#neovim
